    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 5</strong> Evocation</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> cone</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (a small crystal or glass cone)</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p>\n\nYou unleash a blast of cold air. Each creature in a 60-foot Cone [Area of Effect]|XPHB|Cone originating from you makes a Constitution saving throw, taking 8d8 Cold damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one. A creature killed by this spell becomes a frozen statue until it thaws.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> The damage increases by 8d8|5-9|1d8 for each spell slot level above 5.</p>",
